# MOVIE SETTING (Movie Recording)

## COOLING FAN SETTING
This item is also found in the photo menus (page 177).

## EDIT/SAVE CUSTOM SETTING
Options are the same as those for still photography, but settings must be adjusted separately (page 144).

## AUTO UPDATE CUSTOM SETTING
Options are the same as those for still photography, but settings must be adjusted separately (page 144).

## CUSTOM MODE SETTING
Choose whether the current custom settings bank is to be used for still photography or movie recording (page 82).

## WIRELESS COMMUNICATION
This item is also found in the photo menus (page 177).
